title: Next Move
description: After being diagnosed with cancer in 2012, former
IBMA Dobro Player of the Year Phil Leadbetter
made a bucket list of friends and idols he had always wanted to record with, and this album is the realization of that dream!
Huge list of guest artists includes
Joe Diffie, Shawn Camp, Sam Bush, John Cowan, Steve Wariner, Marty Raybon, Bela Fleck, Jerry Douglas

I'm a Ramblin' Rolling Stone I've Never Seen a Love that Wasn't Blind Baptism Just Joshin' Jesus, My Old Dog and Me Hole in the Earth Georgia on My Mind Leadbelly Pull the Trigger I'm a Modern Day Interstate Gypsy Sweet Georgia Brown When the Roll is Called up Yonder

A fantastic collaboration of instrumentalsand vocals from a variety of influences. --Country Standard TimeA living bluegrass legend and first-call Nashvillesession musician, Leadbetter effortlessly dancesfrom graceful melodic and chordal passages tosolo flights remarkable for the way they echo asong s emotional heartbeat. --Gibson.com
